  <brief_title>Short Course Glucocorticoid Treatment for PTSD</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Placebo-controlled, Randomized, Double-blind Comparison of Placebo vs Short Course Low Dose Corticosteroids on Posttraumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
