  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate if a 2-wk course of 20mg/day of oral prednisone
      in addition to standard care will result in reduced PTSD symptoms or symptom severity
      compared to placebo
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
